author: CBS Mornings

description:
A California family living in a fake horror house featured in the hit TV show "American Horror Story" says it's turning into a real-life nightmare. The new owners are suing the former owners and the real estate company because they say they were never told that crowds of obsessive fans travel to see it. Jamie Yuccas reports.
